
Dependencies
============

- python3
- python3-sqlalchemy
- python3-requests


Configuration file
==================

cat ~/.config/ghlister.ini

        [main]
        # see http://docs.sqlalchemy.org/en/latest/core/engines.html#database-urls
        db_url = postgres:///github
        cache_dir = cache
        log_dir = log
        username = foobar
        password = quux
